    public static final String CONST_HELP_JSON = "[{\"mHeader\":\"Change Theme\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>When you switch your device to light or dark theme, Genesis will match your system theme by default. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap General Menu.Tap the theme Mode toggle (blue means it is on)</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_home\"},{\"mHeader\":\"New Tab Settings\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can change new tab settings to open empty tab or default search engine. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap General Menu.Tap the new tab toggle (blue means it is set to open default search engine)</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_advance\"},{\"mHeader\":\"New Identity\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>By click on New Identity, you can change your IP Address. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Click on New Identity then your IP Address will automatically change.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_perm_identity\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Find your Location\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>Find your Location. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Swipe to make genesis notification visible</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>The notification will show your IP and connected country</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_advance\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Remove Notification\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You want to stop all notifications. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Manage Notifications. Off the Network Status and Notifications toggle button.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_notifications\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Change Tab Design\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can change tab view designs. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Advanced Menu. Two radio buttons, choose the Grid Design or List Design</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_new_tab\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Block Images\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can block images (images will not show on screen) if you want. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Advanced Menu.Two radio buttons, choose the always show images or block all images</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_setting\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Manage Search Engine\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can change search engine and set as deafault search engine. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Manage Search Menu</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_search\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Allow Javascripts\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can disable javascripts for various scripts attacks. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Privacy Menu. Switch off the Allow Javascripts toggle.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_privacy\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Zoom & Font Setting\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can change font size and zoom IN/OUT. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Accessibility Menu.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_accessibility\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Clear Data\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can clear all data. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Clear Private Data Button.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_clear\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Manage Cookies & Tracking\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>Orion will tell sites that you do not want to be tracked. You can change cookies preferences according to your security needs by:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Privacy Menu. Select cookies at bottom according to your need.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_privacy\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Publish Website\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can publish your own onion website to our search engine. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top left of the screen (Tor Connection is ON)</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Goto Settings and Tap Publish Website.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_policy\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Disable Tor Proxy\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can enable and disable Tor Proxy. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Restart application and go to Homepage</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Normal browsing to browse without Tor.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Tor browsing to browse with Tor enabled</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_advance\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Change Language\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can change your display language . To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap General Menu.Tap the new tab toggle (blue means it is set to open default search engine)</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_language\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Add Bookmark\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can add websites to your bookmarks. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap star in top row to add opened website in bookmark</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_bookmark\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Bridges Setting\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>Customize bridges. Use only if tor network is blocked in your country. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap setting button ( Make sure tor proxy is running )</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel.</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Customize Bridges.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_advance\"},{\"mHeader\":\"View Logs & Crashes\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can view settings of tor network and orbot connection. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Onion Proxy Status.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_bug\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Factory Reset & Fix App\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>You can fix app and perform a reset if something is wrong with how it performs. To do this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top right of the screen</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Settings in the menu panel</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin-top:1000px;\\\"><strong><p>3. </strong> Tap Fix and Reset and click Reset once the popup shows up</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_repair\"},{\"mHeader\":\"Report Website\",\"mDescription\":\"<p>Orion allows to report any website. To change this:</p><br><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>1.</strong> Tap Menu button at the top left of the screen (Tor Connection is ON)</p><p style=\\\"display: block;margin:1000px;\\\"><strong>2. </strong>Tap Report Website.</p>\",\"mIcon\":\"ic_baseline_report\"}]";

